[7] What happens if you shrink a P54C Pentium to 32nm and call it Quark?， http://semiaccurate.com/2013/09/11/happens-shrink-p54c-pentium-32nm-call-quark/<br />
[8] Intel Quark Soc Datasheet， https://communities.intel.com/docs/DOC-21828<br />
[9] CY8C9520A,CY8C9540A, CY8C9560A,20-, 40-, and 60-Bit I/O Expander with EEPROM datasheet， http://www.cypress.com/?docID=31413<br />
